FBIS4-13672 "drnes078_l_94009" FBIS-NES-94-078 Daily Report 22 Apr 1994 ISRAEL 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam Said Responsible 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam Said Responsible TA2204062494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0600 GMT 22 Apr 94 TA2204062494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Excerpt] An anonymous caller phoned the studio of Israel Television's Arabic department in Jerusalem a short while ago and declared that the 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam organization was responsible for the murder of cadet Shahar Simani. [passage omitted]
